{"tid":1373563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"撤你老母撤你老母撤你老母","createTime":"2019-07-27T15:46:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T16:09:34.000Z","uid":25245,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9e1aaf86a63dadff7aaa92738e5ab5620b18b6fb","tid":1373563,"uid":25245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:46:25.000Z","msg":"下下話有狗就撤 本身去得就預左有狗架啦 係咪傻撚左<br />\n有啲會走嘅一定走<br />\n但你攞住大聲公係咪都鳩嗌要撤，搞到連本身會留會撐住前線嘅人都走撚曬<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咁仲有幾多人會撐得住前線啊</span><br />\n唔該拎大聲公又好傳話又好，淨係講前面有咩事發生<br />\n好多人乜撚都唔知就比你地嚇撚驚左走左 <br />\n咁樣出黎仲有咩意義 行兩行就走根本依家都冇機會發生架啦<br />\n<br />\n仲有 希望在場嘅人 無論衝唔衝，<span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔好</span>人地講一句就跟一句做<br />\n睇清楚發生咩事 以你能力做幾多得幾多好嘛？<br />\nFull gear唔係得個講字 買豬咀頭盔眼罩百令蚊請咁多位手足一定要好好保護自己<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">發夢一定要full gear full gear full gear 啊！</span>"},{"pid":"c8e7682bb6b57c89d1eb60e6f68d0baaf9572f6e","tid":1373563,"uid":25245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:46:41.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"2133d57ec1cf0eccf3019a5ec12fa9e739319568","tid":1373563,"uid":25245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:46:58.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"3200d975a4acd210b77980bf9f1aa90bf10c293a","tid":1373563,"uid":25245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:47:34.000Z","msg":"唔係口講一齊走一齊走"},{"pid":"1a7bf3480e4c5db8707044cac87fea9ee761344d","tid":1373563,"uid":25245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:47:46.000Z","msg":"要做架"},{"pid":"bb269521f265abfc786d82577527709bca18a136","tid":1373563,"uid":25245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:48:04.000Z","msg":"屌 我無嘢講"},{"pid":"de725e86a4b37a6cf3c5c136223cf7c6f4cf687b","tid":1373563,"uid":25245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:48:50.000Z","msg":"gear一人一套"},{"pid":"54323f5127f2e79d51277251d71ec9ad31c38caf","tid":1373563,"uid":25245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s